{"tid":1576263,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"隱藏惡法【導致警隊產生離叛情緒的罰則】","createTime":"2019-09-17T07:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T07:19:57.000Z","uid":145859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"910701128d3fb5a6cbb07dc6a47321a20dd8d7bf","tid":1576263,"uid":145859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:12:12.000Z","msg":"話說，之前睇警隊條例，睇到呢一條：<br />\n第232章 《警隊條例》<br />\n62.導致警隊產生離叛情緒的罰則<br />\n任何人導致、企圖導致或作出任何作為刻意導致警隊成員產生離叛情緒，或誘使或企圖誘使或作出任何作為刻意誘使警隊成員違犯紀律或不再提供服務，即屬犯罪，循簡易程序定罪後，可處罰款$2,000及監禁2年。<br />\n(由1950年第29號第16條增補)<br />\n<br />\n大家睇路呀，無謂多條例比人拉！雖然而家都係莫須有。<br />\n利申：無法律background，求法律界人士補充"},{"pid":"d56dd03d01810c7b9df65bd48ae9e0d9a811769d","tid":1576263,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:12:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【922攻略流出】<br />\n907<span style=\"color: gold;\">加強版</span>配合hkmap live <br />\n更「大局」交通測試，彩虹戰衣、影帝、機巴、塞鐵、嶄新突擊RB、私家車傾巢而出，裡應外合 <br />\n+機場員工集體Call Sick <br />\n+雷達站/機場附近新搞作<br />\n+大量中港貨櫃司機加入物資支援！<br />\n<br />\n更多攻略，陸續公布，敬請留意"},{"pid":"e568789688e066947bc0c14975022af6c2741e10","tid":1576263,"uid":24465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:13:06.000Z","msg":"好on9<br />\n軍政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9b9684091045ce85aebe1970d04c9ac6522e65","tid":1576263,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:13:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oXFigFX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoXFigFX.png&h=4d54545f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae4cddb957f945d653930b92785c9d5b136643b9","tid":1576263,"uid":18271,"like"